isMult

private static boolean isMult(ExprBinary.Op op,
                              Expr left,
                              Expr right)
Determines whether the expression (left op right) is an arrow multiplicity constraint.
That means it is of the form (A ?->? B), or it is (A->B) where A and/or B is an arrow multiplicity constraint.
